QueryToExecute:
select
  arn as resource,
  case
    when max_user_duration_in_seconds < 36000 then 'ok'
    else 'alarm'
  end as status,
  title || ' max user duration in seconds is set to ' || max_user_duration_in_seconds || ' seconds.' as reason
  
  , region, account_id
from
  aws_appstream_fleet;
